TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: This lookup in conjunction with the parameter APC_STAT_CD (from TDISCNT_PERIOD) is used to determine if the INV_ID/HVST_ID is pre-APC/APC/post-APC. There is a SQL override in the lookup, which has all model Harvest IDs in it, However, for any given run, ONLY 1 of the model hvst IDs will have a valid value, the others will be 0.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_SNAP_APC_STAT_CD

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT MAX(SNP.SNAP_APC_TYP_CD) AS SNAP_APC_STAT_CD, DTL.HVST_ID as HVST_ID, DTL.INV_ID as INV_ID FROM VRAP.TSNAP_INV_DTL DTL, VRAP.TSNAP SNP WHERE DTL.HVST_ID in ($$DSC_HVST_IDs, $$GPO_HVST_IDs, $$XMD_HVST_IDs) AND DTL.SNAP_ID = SNP.SNAP_ID AND SNP.SNAP_SEQ_NB > 0 GROUP BY DTL.HVST_ID, DTL.INV_ID

SESSION.DESCRIPTION: Session executes only if there are XMD HVST IDs to process. Loads claims for the specific XMD Hvst IDs to the staging table. Joins and filters are overridden in the session. There are lookups with sql overrides and filters.
SESSION.NAME: s_m_CASH_Load_RCNT_RECN_EXTN_CLM_STG_XMD_CopyVoid

ATTRIBUTE.NAME: User Defined Join
ATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
--joins are overridden in the session
VRAP.RCIT_CLM_INV_ELIG.CLM_GID = VRAP.TDISCNT_EXT_CLAIM_XMD.CLAIM_ID AND VRAP.RCIT_CLM_INV_ELIG.EXTL_SRC_CD = VRAP.TDISCNT_EXT_CLAIM_XMD.EXTNL_SRC_CD

ATTRIBUTE.NAME: Source Filter
ATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
-- filters are overridden in the session
VRAP.TDISCNT_EXT_CLAIM_XMD.HVST_ID IN ($$XMD_HVST_IDs) AND VRAP.TDISCNT_EXT_CLAIM_XMD.PERIOD_ID = '$$PERIOD_ID' AND VRAP.RCIT_CLM_INV_ELIG.INV_ELIG_DT BETWEEN '$$INV_ELIG_STRT_DT' AND '$$INV_ELIG_END_DT' AND VRAP.RCIT_CLM_INV_ELIG.MODEL_TYP_CD = 'X'

ATTRIBUTE.NAME: Source Filter
ATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
-- filters are overridden in the session
VRAP.RCNT_RBAT_MFG_INV_DTL.HVST_ID in ($$XMD_HVST_IDs) AND VRAP.RCNT_RBAT_MFG_INV_DTL.MODEL_TYP_CD = 'X' AND VRAP.RCNT_RBAT_MFG_INV_HDR.RECN_GID IN ($$RECN_GIDs) AND VRAP.RCNT_RBAT_MFG_INV_HDR.INV_STAT_CD = 1

ATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Source Filter
ATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
--filter overridden in the session
HVST_ID in ($$XMD_HVST_IDs) AND RECN_GID in ($$RECN_GIDs) AND RECN_SCRB_CD <> 99

ATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
ATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT TXMD.HVST_ID AS HVST_ID , TXMD.RPT_DRUG_ID AS RPT_DRUG_ID , MAX(TXMD.MKSR_RATE_VL) AS MKSR_RATE_VL , MAX(TXMD.BASE_RATE_VL) AS BASE_RATE_VL , MAX(TXMD.ADMN_RATE_VL) AS ADMN_RATE_VL FROM VRAP.TDISCNT_RPT_DRUG_TIER_XMD TXMD WHERE TXMD.HVST_ID IN ($$XMD_HVST_IDs) GROUP BY TXMD.HVST_ID, TXMD.RPT_DRUG_ID
